===Wildlife sanctuaries===
There are three wildlife sanctuaries, two of which are in [[Protected Areas Regional Offices of Thailand|region 8 (Khon Kaen)]], and Phu Khat in [[Protected Areas Regional Offices of Thailand|region 11 (Phitsanulok)]] of Thailand's protected areas.
